The paper focuses on studying the behavioral dynamics of bots and humans on social media, which falls under the category of social computing (cs.SI) and data mining (cs.SD). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms for bot detection, which could be categorized under cybersecurity (cs.CR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
